# UI Guidelines

## Theme — use ContextExtension, never Theme.of()

```dart
// ✅ Correct
context.textTheme.titleMedium
context.colorScheme.primary
context.colorScheme.surfaceBright

// ❌ Never
Theme.of(context).textTheme.titleMedium
```

## Spacing and sizing — AppDimensions only

```dart
// ✅ Correct
padding: EdgeInsets.all(AppDimensions.paddingMedium)
borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(AppDimensions.radiusMedium)
minimumSize: Size.fromHeight(AppDimensions.buttonHeight)

// ❌ Never
padding: EdgeInsets.all(16)
```

## Colors — colorScheme / AppColors only

```dart
// ✅ Correct
color: context.colorScheme.error
color: AppColors.brand

// ❌ Never
color: Color(0xFFE53935)
```

## Screen dimensions — ContextExtension shortcuts

```dart
context.sw           // MediaQuery screen width
context.sh           // MediaQuery screen height
context.topPadding   // Safe-area top inset
context.bottomPadding
```

## Dialogs — BlocListener only

Show all `AppDialog` calls inside `BlocListener`, never inside `BlocBuilder` or `build()`.

```dart
// ✅ Correct placement
BlocListener<MyCubit, DefaultState<MyModel>>(
  listener: (context, state) {
    state.when(
      loading: AppDialog.showLoading,
      success: (_) { AppDialog.dismiss(); },
      fail: (f) { AppDialog.dismiss(); AppDialog.showError(message: f.message); },
      init: () {},
    );
  },
  child: ...,
)
```
